164
00:08:57.864 --> 00:09:01.404
off, not on. Rather, the T cell gets a sense of context from the target through the

165
00:09:01.424 --> 00:09:04.304
expression of other molecules that are seen as the T cell kisses up against its

166
00:09:04.314 --> 00:09:08.213
target. It gets instructions about the nature of that

