00:10:21.484 --> 00:10:22.054
all of the

189
00:10:22.124 --> 00:11:11.244
co-stimulatory

190
00:11:11.254 --> 00:11:14.914
signals and subtracting out all the co-inhibitory signals and

191
00:11:14.924 --> 00:11:17.464
deciding what to do at that moment.

192
00:11:17.484 --> 00:11:21.324
But the key thing I want you to take away from this talk, as we're going to get a

193
00:11:21.364 --> 00:11:24.844
