00:11:40.564 --> 00:11:42.404
That's going to be very clear to understand later.

199
00:11:43.564 --> 00:11:46.044
Now, this was coined by Liping Chen,

200
00:11:47.004 --> 00:11:49.844
a molecular shield that happens in cancer.

