00:12:26.432 --> 00:12:28.432
learned, and I hate to personify them, but here we are,

212
00:12:29.372 --> 00:12:33.252
to upregulate the ligands for co-inhibitory molecules and down-regulate the

213
00:12:33.272 --> 00:12:37.152
ligands for co-stimulatory molecules, becoming invisible,

214
00:12:37.212 --> 00:12:41.132
if you will, to the immune system. The first and most prolific of these that

215
00:12:41.172 --> 00:12:44.952
was discovered was called B7H1. It is now known

