00:14:10.752 --> 00:14:14.452
So when T cells come in, they secrete gamma interferon, the tumor

239
00:14:14.532 --> 00:14:18.372
cell senses the gamma interferon and upregulates this receptor.

240
00:14:18.712 --> 00:14:22.592
So it's a response to being seen by the T cell in the

