242
00:14:26.592 --> 00:14:29.692
other name for PDL1, if you just give it recombinant gamma

243
00:14:29.712 --> 00:14:33.492
interferon, it turns up PDL1 both at the level on the cell

244
00:14:33.532 --> 00:14:35.192
surface as well as

245
00:14:37.052 --> 00:14:38.292
by message.

246
00:14:39.472 --> 00:14:41.232
But it's not only gamma interferon.

247
00:14:41.312 --> 00:14:45.122
Things like DNA damage, hypoxia, type 1 interferons,

248
00:14:45.532 --> 00:14:49.362
many other features can upregulate the expression of this ligand on

249
00:14:49.392 --> 00:14:52.812
tumor cells. But this isn't just tumor cells.

250
00:14:53.512 --> 00:14:57.312
Any nucleated cell, if you tickle it with gamma interferon and TNF and

251
00:14:57.392 --> 00:15:01.372
other molecules, it will turn on PDL1, and thus

252
00:15:01.452 --> 00:15:04.032
this is not necessarily tumor specific.

253
00:15:04.292 --> 00:15:08.172
This is something that PDL1 does is to turn

254
00:15:08.292 --> 00:15:08.552
off

255
00:15:09.732 --> 00:15:11.592
T cells when they get hyperactive.

256
00:15:12.072 --> 00:15:14.962
