But nowadays, we have a lot of antibody treatments

479
00:28:10.476 --> 00:28:13.796
against rheumatoid arthritis, against TNF-alpha, IL6,

480
00:28:14.656 --> 00:28:16.396
IL8, name it.

481
00:28:17.796 --> 00:28:21.676
Do you have any idea if those patients have a higher rate of cancer, too, or they

482
00:28:21.696 --> 00:28:24.016
are more specific and that doesn't happen?

483
00:28:24.416 --> 00:28:28.336
Yeah. It depends on the type of blocker, but if you

484
00:28:29.016 --> 00:28:31.886
listen to the fine print that the announcer is reading during all those

485
00:28:31.896 --> 00:28:32.796
commercials, right?

486
00:28:33.606 --> 00:28:33.606
Right.

487
00:28:34.676 --> 00:28:36.256
That's happening at the end of a commercial.

