00:33:50.788 --> 00:33:54.028
cell. So how do they do that? I'll just remind you, I know that we just talked

583
00:33:54.088 --> 00:33:57.888
about that, but these cancer cells have the ability to

584
00:33:57.928 --> 00:34:01.688
process protein, chop it up into pieces, and present

